<div class="mb-4">
  <h1 class="h3">管理者ダッシュボード</h1>
  <p class="text-muted mb-0">登録ユーザーの確認と退会処理を行えます。</p>
</div>

<div class="row g-3 mb-4">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="text-muted mb-1">ユーザー数</p>
        <p class="display-6 mb-0"><%= @users_count %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="text-muted mb-1">投稿数</p>
        <p class="display-6 mb-0"><%= @posts_count %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="text-muted mb-1">コメント数</p>
        <p class="display-6 mb-0"><%= @comments_count %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div>
  <%= link_to "ユーザー一覧を見る", admin_users_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
</div>